data.title: The Philippines New SWF has Grand Ambitions, but Needs Co-Investors and Foreign Capital (GlobalSWF)
data.meta_description: The Philippines’ sovereign wealth fund, the Maharlika Investment Corporation (MIC), is now firmly established and about to originate deals for the Maharlika Investment Fund (MIF) focusing on domestic infrastructure and impact investment.
data.text:
The Philippines’ sovereign wealth fund, the Maharlika Investment Corporation (MIC), is now firmly established and about to originate deals for the Maharlika Investment Fund (MIF) focusing on domestic infrastructure and impact investment.Last month, the MIC’s board approved the investment and risk management frameworks that will govern the MIF, covering “detailed policies, strategies,...
